<div xml:space="preserve">
<p begin="74400000t" end="97600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle0">(還能爭取多少自由)</p>
<p begin="181200000t" end="220000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle1">「約定的夢幻島」</p>
<p begin="253200000t" end="262000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle2">(Fire)</p>
<p begin="268400000t" end="290800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle3">(該我出場了　率先上陣)</p>
<p begin="291600000t" end="315200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle4">(在知道何謂失敗之前)</p>
<p begin="316000000t" end="344000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle5">(先找到導火線)</p>
<p begin="344800000t" end="356400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle6">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="357200000t" end="386400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle7">(沒有神明可崇拜　也沒有星星)</p>
<p begin="387200000t" end="412400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle8">(但是從沒放棄祈求)</p>
<p begin="413200000t" end="440000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle9">(因害怕後悔而停滯的腳步)</p>
<p begin="440800000t" end="450800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle10">(朝它Fire)</p>
<p begin="451600000t" end="499200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle11">(想忘記的正是無法忘掉的事)</p>
<p begin="500000000t" end="546000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle12">(通往天堂之路始於地獄)</p>
<p begin="546800000t" end="593600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle13">(一點火花化為熊熊烈火)</p>
<p begin="594400000t" end="627200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle14">(緊張不安地不斷追趕)</p>
<p begin="628000000t" end="651600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle15">(奔往未來)</p>
<p begin="652390000t" end="674000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle16">(儘管只是數厘米)</p>
<p begin="674800000t" end="697600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle17">(也要朝著願望中的目的地)</p>
<p begin="698400000t" end="721200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle18">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="749200000t" end="795600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle19">(為內心贖罪　勸自己放棄)</p>
<p begin="796400000t" end="816800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle20">(這樣將來還能說甚麼)</p>
<p begin="843200000t" end="864800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle21">(不斷前行　不要停步)</p>
<p begin="912400000t" end="931600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle22">你以後就用這個房間</p>
<p begin="938000000t" end="950400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle23">是，我知道了</p>
<p begin="961200000t" end="979600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle24">她住在這裡對我們很不利</p>
<p begin="988000000t" end="1012400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle25">還要住在三間小朋友房的中間</p>
<p begin="1016400000t" end="1034000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle26">這是為了方便監視我們</p>
<p begin="1140400000t" end="1158800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle27">將注意力都放在發訊器上</p>
<p begin="1159600000t" end="1178000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle28">完全沒想過會增加了一個成人</p>
<p begin="1186000000t" end="1202400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle29">相反，我們應該覺得開心</p>
<p begin="1211600000t" end="1224000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle30">覺得開心？</p>
<p begin="1224800000t" end="1248800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle31">卡洛和那個克羅妮修女來了</p>
<p begin="1249600000t" end="1271200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle32">這就代表情報來源增加了兩個</p>
<p begin="1279200000t" end="1292400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle33">原來如此</p>
<p begin="1293200000t" end="1314400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle34">她們是從哪裡來的</p>
<p begin="1324800000t" end="1349200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle35">卡洛是來取代柯妮的</p>
<p begin="1350000000t" end="1369200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle36">換言之，即是商品的補充</p>
<p begin="1370000000t" end="1396000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle37">沒錯，如果這裡是農場</p>
<p begin="1396800000t" end="1410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle38">就代表外面有一個</p>
<p begin="1410800000t" end="1429200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle39">可以持續提供一歲幼兒的據點</p>
<p begin="1439600000t" end="1454400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle40">即是我們所有人</p>
<p begin="1455200000t" end="1474000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle41">本來都是從那個地方來的？</p>
<p begin="1474800000t" end="1484000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle42">應該是</p>
<p begin="1490400000t" end="1509600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle43">而且那個克羅妮修女也一樣</p>
<p begin="1515600000t" end="1528800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle44">除了媽媽以外</p>
<p begin="1529600000t" end="1552000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle45">還有其他成年人這點也很重要</p>
<p begin="1552800000t" end="1565600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle46">說不定還有其他</p>
<p begin="1566400000t" end="1586000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle47">像這裡這樣的農場</p>
<p begin="1588000000t" end="1605200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle48">那些服從鬼的成年人</p>
<p begin="1606000000t" end="1628400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle49">是從出生開始就受到鬼的支配嗎</p>
<p begin="1633600000t" end="1654800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle50">還是被鬼捉了才變成這樣</p>
<p begin="1655600000t" end="1666800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle51">根據這個差異</p>
<p begin="1667600000t" end="1684400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle52">外面的世界將會完全不同</p>
<p begin="1685200000t" end="1702800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle53">但是我們首先應該考慮</p>
<p begin="1703600000t" end="1721600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle54">怎樣帶著全部人逃走</p>
<p begin="1722400000t" end="1742400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle55">以及發訊器的位置</p>
<p begin="1749200000t" end="1773600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle56">那次之後，我找遍全身每個部位</p>
<p begin="1774400000t" end="1795600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle57">都找不到植入發訊器的痕跡</p>
<p begin="1796400000t" end="1814400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle58">連衣服和鞋子都沒有</p>
<p begin="1820800000t" end="1853600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle59">如果從人類科學技術常識的角度看</p>
<p begin="1854400000t" end="1874000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle60">有可能是利用無線電波的發訊器</p>
<p begin="1879200000t" end="1892000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle61">但是這就需要用電池</p>
<p begin="1900000000t" end="1919200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle62">要有十年以上的電池壽命</p>
<p begin="1920000000t" end="1942400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle63">又不會留下手術痕跡的超小型裝置</p>
<p begin="1950000000t" end="1968400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle64">以當時2015年來說</p>
<p begin="1969200000t" end="1984000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle65">應該沒可能做得出這樣的東西</p>
<p begin="1994000000t" end="2005200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle66">即是說…</p>
<p begin="2006000000t" end="2022400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle67">以它的運作原理</p>
<p begin="2023200000t" end="2048400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle68">推斷出位置和破壞方法是很難的事</p>
<p begin="2055600000t" end="2065200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle69">更何況…</p>
<p begin="2066000000t" end="2078400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle70">如果是鬼的獨有技術</p>
<p begin="2079200000t" end="2088800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle71">那就沒辦法了</p>
<p begin="2089600000t" end="2098000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle72">沒錯</p>
<p begin="2116400000t" end="2124000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle73">沒辦法了嗎</p>
<p begin="2130400000t" end="2140400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle74">沒辦法了</p>
<p begin="2141200000t" end="2154400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle75">這次糟糕了</p>
<p begin="2155200000t" end="2179200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle76">就算不知道運作原理</p>
<p begin="2180000000t" end="2191600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle77">也可以推斷線索</p>
<p begin="2192400000t" end="2224800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle78">沒錯，要以敵人的角度來思考</p>
<p begin="2225600000t" end="2242400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle79">到底在哪裡植入怎樣的發訊器</p>
<p begin="2243200000t" end="2255200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle80">比較方便</p>
<p begin="2352800000t" end="2360800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle81">卡洛</p>
<p begin="2372800000t" end="2394800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle82">這個剛剛來的女嬰身上可能會有</p>
<p begin="2408400000t" end="2426800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle83">植入發訊器的手術痕跡</p>
<p begin="2460400000t" end="2480000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle84">真的很感謝你這次給我機會</p>
<p begin="2480800000t" end="2497600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle85">讓我可以再回來這邊</p>
<p begin="2498400000t" end="2518800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle86">我只不過是申請了一個助手</p>
<p begin="2519600000t" end="2530000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle87">過來幫忙而已</p>
<p begin="2530800000t" end="2552000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle88">我並沒有特別指定說要找你</p>
<p begin="2558000000t" end="2579200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle89">我曾聽過關於前輩的傳聞</p>
<p begin="2580000000t" end="2597200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle90">以最小的年紀被提拔</p>
<p begin="2598000000t" end="2616000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle91">成為媽媽的養育監</p>
<p begin="2616800000t" end="2636400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle92">培養出頂級品的數量</p>
<p begin="2637200000t" end="2661200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle93">更是所有養育場的歷代之冠</p>
<p begin="2662000000t" end="2689600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle94">可以在我尊敬的前輩帶領下工作</p>
<p begin="2690400000t" end="2705600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle95">我真的覺得很光榮</p>
<p begin="2706400000t" end="2723600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle96">客套說話可以免了</p>
<p begin="2732400000t" end="2752400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle97">不要再說廢話</p>
<p begin="2753200000t" end="2768000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle98">快點開始說工作的事</p>
<p begin="2783200000t" end="2809200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle99">這些就是我可愛的小朋友的資料</p>
<p begin="2816000000t" end="2835600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle100">立即給我在這裡記進腦裡</p>
<p begin="2842800000t" end="2875600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle101">這樣應該比每天早上找滿分更容易</p>
<p begin="2912400000t" end="2921200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle102">還有一個問題</p>
<p begin="2922000000t" end="2951200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle103">不知道我是被派來負責甚麼工作呢</p>
<p begin="2952000000t" end="2963200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle104">有人發現了秘密</p>
<p begin="2980400000t" end="2997600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle105">貨車的貨台也被人看到了</p>
<p begin="3007200000t" end="3030400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle106">那就按照規定把這個人找出來</p>
<p begin="3031200000t" end="3050800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle107">即時出欄　　慢著，等等</p>
<p begin="3126000000t" end="3134800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle108">沒事的</p>
<p begin="3135600000t" end="3158400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle109">我已經大概猜到目標人物是誰</p>
<p begin="3164000000t" end="3176000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle110">那他是…</p>
<p begin="3176800000t" end="3195600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle111">年齡較大的兩個小朋友</p>
<p begin="3200000000t" end="3209600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle112">只要在出欄之前</p>
<p begin="3210400000t" end="3231200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle113">不要讓他們逃掉就沒問題</p>
<p begin="3232000000t" end="3242000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle114">因為我的小朋友</p>
<p begin="3242800000t" end="3256800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle115">每一個都很特別</p>
<p begin="3257600000t" end="3282000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle116">這件事關乎到養育場的利益</p>
<p begin="3282800000t" end="3314800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle117">那即是不用向上級報告嗎　　不用</p>
<p begin="3315600000t" end="3337200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle118">我會採用適當程序處理目標人物</p>
<p begin="3344000000t" end="3356000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle119">你就負責監視</p>
<p begin="3364400000t" end="3388000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle120">甚麼都不用想，監視他們就可以了</p>
<p begin="3404800000t" end="3431200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle121">你要記著這間孤兒院的媽媽是我</p>
<p begin="3432000000t" end="3452400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle122">而你就只是我的一個助手</p>
<p begin="3459200000t" end="3481200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle123">有甚麼不明白的嗎？克羅妮修女</p>
<p begin="3486800000t" end="3512400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle124">完全明白，伊薩貝拉女士</p>
<p begin="3532400000t" end="3548400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle125">不就是嗎</p>
<p begin="3549200000t" end="3572400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle126">其實我也一樣覺得很驚訝</p>
<p begin="3573200000t" end="3588000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle127">想不到那個平時</p>
<p begin="3588800000t" end="3615600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle128">表現得非常優秀的伊薩貝拉</p>
<p begin="3616400000t" end="3633200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle129">竟然會不向上級報告</p>
<p begin="3634000000t" end="3662000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle130">而且還打算要掩藏自己的過失</p>
<p begin="3662800000t" end="3690000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle131">但是只要我現在幫她的忙</p>
<p begin="3690800000t" end="3706000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle132">她就會欠我一個人情</p>
<p begin="3706800000t" end="3731200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle133">有朝一日，我也會坐上媽媽寶座</p>
<p begin="3754800000t" end="3770000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle134">怎麼了</p>
<p begin="3770800000t" end="3801200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle135">為甚麼哭得這麼大聲、這麼淒涼</p>
<p begin="3802000000t" end="3824000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle136">很乖，不要哭</p>
<p begin="3824800000t" end="3838800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle137">我成為媽媽的話</p>
<p begin="3839600000t" end="3859200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle138">你也會替我開心，對嗎</p>
<p begin="3860000000t" end="3883600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle139">雖然到時會變得比現在更忙</p>
<p begin="3884400000t" end="3912800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle140">但是你也會繼續支持我，對嗎</p>
<p begin="3913600000t" end="3933200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle141">你不可以妒忌其他小朋友</p>
<p begin="3934000000t" end="3963600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle142">還有不准任性和不准鬧彆扭</p>
<p begin="3964400000t" end="4007600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle143">等等，莫非這個…是我的機會</p>
<p begin="4008400000t" end="4037200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle144">這是我成為媽媽的機會</p>
<p begin="4038000000t" end="4074400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle145">不用等有朝一日，現在就是了</p>
<p begin="4083600000t" end="4113600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle146">因為只要我捉住知道秘密的小朋友</p>
<p begin="4114400000t" end="4135600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle147">然後告發這個違規行為</p>
<p begin="4136400000t" end="4164800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle148">伊薩貝拉就會被人開除</p>
<p begin="4165600000t" end="4189200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle149">既然這樣，我假扮聽從她的吩咐</p>
<p begin="4190000000t" end="4208000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle150">之後再搶走她的媽媽寶座</p>
<p begin="4208800000t" end="4224000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle151">這不是更快嗎</p>
<p begin="4224800000t" end="4284800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle152">捉住目標人物，告發他</p>
<p begin="4285600000t" end="4321200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle153">讓他立即出欄</p>
<p begin="4344400000t" end="4375600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle154">太好了，我將會成為這裡的媽媽</p>
<p begin="4376400000t" end="4403200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle155">要儘快找他們出來才行</p>
<p begin="4441600000t" end="4456800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle156">她很受小朋友歡迎</p>
<p begin="4465200000t" end="4490000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle157">對，究竟怎樣才可以</p>
<p begin="4490800000t" end="4510400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle158">瞞著兩個受小朋友歡迎的成年人</p>
<p begin="4523600000t" end="4548400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle159">就是了，現在最麻煩的事</p>
<p begin="4549200000t" end="4563200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle160">就是她們會向鬼通報</p>
<p begin="4568800000t" end="4583200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle161">只要我們一開始逃走</p>
<p begin="4584000000t" end="4600000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle162">就會立即被怪物追捕</p>
<p begin="4600800000t" end="4617600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle163">還有一個方法可以阻止他們</p>
<p begin="4626400000t" end="4640000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle164">就是將媽媽和那個修女…</p>
<p begin="4729200000t" end="4763200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle165">你們就是諾曼和阿雷嗎　　是</p>
<p begin="4784000000t" end="4826400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle166">聽說你們的測驗拿滿分　　是</p>
<p begin="4827200000t" end="4854800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle167">很厲害，請多多指教</p>
<p begin="4855600000t" end="4872000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle168">我們要好好相處</p>
<p begin="4990400000t" end="5015200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle169">讓她聽到了？　　沒…沒事的</p>
<p begin="5020800000t" end="5038000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle170">這個修女來這裡</p>
<p begin="5038800000t" end="5066000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle171">似乎不只是為了監視我們那麼簡單</p>
<p begin="5066800000t" end="5080000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle172">這樣說是甚麼意思</p>
<p begin="5080800000t" end="5098800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle173">她看我們的眼神不同</p>
<p begin="5099600000t" end="5110400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle174">一定是懷疑我們</p>
<p begin="5116000000t" end="5132400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle175">年齡比較大的小朋友</p>
<p begin="5133200000t" end="5162800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle176">她從哪裡得到這些情報</p>
<p begin="5169190000t" end="5190800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle177">這還用說嗎？當然是媽媽</p>
<p begin="5203600000t" end="5213200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle178">媽媽的魔掌</p>
<p begin="5218400000t" end="5236400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle179">確實正慢慢地逼近我們</p>
<p begin="5243200000t" end="5253200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle180">要快些才行</p>
<p begin="5378800000t" end="5407600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle181">要從敵人的角度來思考</p>
<p begin="5415200000t" end="5446800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle182">那些鬼又不會吃發訊器，所以…</p>
<p begin="5454400000t" end="5466800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle183">在一個容易拿出來的地方</p>
<p begin="5467600000t" end="5488400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle184">艾瑪，我有一件事…</p>
<p begin="5489200000t" end="5512800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle185">在哪裡　　我有一件事想問你</p>
<p begin="5518800000t" end="5532800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle186">那天晚上</p>
<p begin="5606400000t" end="5625200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle187">是甚麼？被蟲咬過？</p>
<p begin="5632800000t" end="5642000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle188">以前媽媽…</p>
<p begin="5648400000t" end="5670000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle189">說過這是我們在身體檢查的時候</p>
<p begin="5670800000t" end="5685600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle190">抽血留下的痕跡</p>
<p begin="5714800000t" end="5734400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle191">我記得奈拉、菲爾、馬克</p>
<p begin="5735200000t" end="5753600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle192">和柯妮的耳朵都有</p>
<p begin="5756800000t" end="5782400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle193">大家的耳朵都有　　我有嗎</p>
<p begin="5810400000t" end="5824800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle194">我們那些消失了</p>
<p begin="5832800000t" end="5850000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle195">消失了也很正常</p>
<p begin="5850800000t" end="5862400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle196">現在我已經10歲</p>
<p begin="5863200000t" end="5880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle197">而艾瑪你已經11歲了</p>
<p begin="5890000000t" end="5919200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle198">這個痕跡真的比我想像中的小得多</p>
<p begin="5920000000t" end="5927600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle199">甚麼</p>
<p begin="5943600000t" end="5965200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle200">沒有，我在想這個傷痕很小</p>
<p begin="5966000000t" end="5980000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle201">所以完全消失了</p>
<p begin="6121200000t" end="6142800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle202">一定要保護這班小朋友</p>
<p begin="6184800000t" end="6204400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle203">定期聯絡…</p>
<p begin="6211600000t" end="6234400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle204">我是73584，第三養育場</p>
<p begin="6243200000t" end="6268800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle205">10月17日，一切正常</p>
<p begin="6269600000t" end="6283600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle206">現在中斷通訊</p>
<p begin="6288800000t" end="6312800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle207">(伊薩貝拉)　　祖母大人？</p>
<p begin="6313600000t" end="6335600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle208">(首領託我傳個口信給你)</p>
<p begin="6342000000t" end="6358400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle209">(之前提過的那三隻)</p>
<p begin="6359200000t" end="6375600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle210">(可否按計劃出欄)</p>
<p begin="6390800000t" end="6412000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle211">(你聽著，伊薩貝拉)</p>
<p begin="6412800000t" end="6424400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle212">(今年整體來說)</p>
<p begin="6425200000t" end="6445600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle213">(其他養育場的收成都不好)</p>
<p begin="6452000000t" end="6466400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle214">(現在能在儀祭上)</p>
<p begin="6467200000t" end="6485600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle215">(奉獻的最佳高級品)</p>
<p begin="6486400000t" end="6514000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle216">(有貨出欄的就只有你的養育場)</p>
<p begin="6514800000t" end="6536400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle217">是，我已經知道這件事</p>
<p begin="6543600000t" end="6577200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle218">請你向首領轉達，一切順利</p>
<p begin="6578000000t" end="6603200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle219">每個兒童都可以隨時出欄</p>
<p begin="6604000000t" end="6628400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle220">是嗎？可以隨時出欄嗎</p>
<p begin="6629200000t" end="6641600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle221">那位大人知道了</p>
<p begin="6642400000t" end="6660400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle222">也一定會覺得很高興</p>
<p begin="6661200000t" end="6676000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle223">不要鬆懈</p>
<p begin="6676800000t" end="6700000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle224">那位大人的膳食要特別準備</p>
<p begin="6700800000t" end="6716000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle225">跟我們的不一樣</p>
<p begin="6723600000t" end="6760000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle226">好，各位，我們一起慶祝收穫</p>
<p begin="6773600000t" end="6804800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle227">來，為那位大人獻上禱告</p>
<p begin="7019600000t" end="7041600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle228">這樣的確很難察覺</p>
<p begin="7047200000t" end="7056400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle229">我也是第一次知道</p>
<p begin="7057200000t" end="7071600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle230">有抽血痕跡的說法</p>
<p begin="7076800000t" end="7098000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle231">這種傷痕這麼快就會消失嗎</p>
<p begin="7114000000t" end="7142400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle232">一直以來，我從來沒懷疑過這點</p>
<p begin="7148800000t" end="7166400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle233">對不起　　不用道歉</p>
<p begin="7167200000t" end="7182400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle234">這是你的功勞</p>
<p begin="7183200000t" end="7204000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle235">現在我們已經知道發訊器的位置</p>
<p begin="7204800000t" end="7217200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle236">形狀和大小</p>
<p begin="7218000000t" end="7228400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle237">可以進行下一步</p>
<p begin="7236400000t" end="7249600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle238">位置之後就是…</p>
<p begin="7260000000t" end="7269200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle239">破壞方法…</p>
<p begin="7276000000t" end="7284400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle240">怎樣做才好</p>
<p begin="7285200000t" end="7305600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle241">就算我們割開耳朵來調查</p>
<p begin="7306400000t" end="7328400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle242">但是如果媽媽撥起頭髮</p>
<p begin="7329200000t" end="7341600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle243">就會立即識破</p>
<p begin="7342400000t" end="7361200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle244">沒錯，首先</p>
<p begin="7362000000t" end="7388800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle245">不管我們是否有辦法輕易破壞它</p>
<p begin="7389600000t" end="7410000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle246">其實植入在耳朵裡的發訊器</p>
<p begin="7410800000t" end="7426000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle247">它的功能很簡單</p>
<p begin="7433200000t" end="7446400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle248">只是很簡單？</p>
<p begin="7447200000t" end="7455600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle249">因為它沒辦法</p>
<p begin="7456400000t" end="7471200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle250">可以區分每一個人的訊號</p>
<p begin="7476800000t" end="7488000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle251">不主動確認的話</p>
<p begin="7488800000t" end="7500400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle252">就連位置也不知道</p>
<p begin="7501200000t" end="7516800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle253">就算接近門或者牆壁</p>
<p begin="7517600000t" end="7527200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle254">都不會發出通知</p>
<p begin="7539200000t" end="7554800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle255">但始終植入了身體</p>
<p begin="7561200000t" end="7575600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle256">是，為甚麼</p>
<p begin="7580800000t" end="7601600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle257">只要發訊器沒有壞，無論在哪裡</p>
<p begin="7602400000t" end="7617200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle258">他們都有信心追蹤到我們</p>
<p begin="7631600000t" end="7651600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle259">等等，這即是說</p>
<p begin="7652400000t" end="7670800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle260">如果它懂得發出通知的話</p>
<p begin="7671600000t" end="7690800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle261">時機就是在發訊器被破壞時？</p>
<p begin="7691600000t" end="7708800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle262">也不排除有這樣的可能性</p>
<p begin="7709600000t" end="7718000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle263">即是怎樣</p>
<p begin="7723200000t" end="7740000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle264">只有在被破壞時</p>
<p begin="7740800000t" end="7757600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle265">發訊器才會發出警報之類</p>
<p begin="7758400000t" end="7766400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle266">立即通知他們</p>
<p begin="7774800000t" end="7798800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle267">破壞了發訊器，媽媽會立即知道？</p>
<p begin="7799600000t" end="7821600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle268">是，但前提是要有通知功能</p>
<p begin="7833600000t" end="7852400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle269">但是考慮到媽媽</p>
<p begin="7853200000t" end="7874000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle270">刻意令我們知道有發訊器這樣東西</p>
<p begin="7874800000t" end="7902000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle271">就不可以輕易否定這點</p>
<p begin="7902800000t" end="7922400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle272">即是隨便用手破壞它也有危險</p>
<p begin="7930400000t" end="7952800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle273">要等逃走時才破壞它</p>
<p begin="7962000000t" end="7990000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle274">但是我們怎麼知道破壞的方法</p>
<p begin="7990800000t" end="8004400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle275">關於這個問題</p>
<p begin="8010000000t" end="8024000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle276">這種形狀和大小</p>
<p begin="8028800000t" end="8042800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle277">我也有一點頭緒</p>
<p begin="8050000000t" end="8073200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle278">可否將這件事交給我處理</p>
<p begin="8085200000t" end="8099600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle279">真的可以？　　是</p>
<p begin="8110400000t" end="8138800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle280">既然阿雷這麼說，就交給你了</p>
<p begin="8146400000t" end="8172400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle281">之後就是帶全部人逃走的方法</p>
<p begin="8178400000t" end="8185200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle282">問題是現在</p>
<p begin="8186000000t" end="8204000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle283">所有小朋友都很信任媽媽</p>
<p begin="8211600000t" end="8244400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle284">而且他們知道事實之後會承受不住</p>
<p begin="8245200000t" end="8264800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle285">是否只可以說謊</p>
<p begin="8265600000t" end="8282000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle286">才能帶他們一起走</p>
<p begin="8282800000t" end="8296800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle287">還有就是他們</p>
<p begin="8297600000t" end="8312800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle288">根本沒足夠的能力</p>
<p begin="8313600000t" end="8334400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle289">簡單來說就是負累</p>
<p begin="8335200000t" end="8348000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle290">阿雷</p>
<p begin="8348800000t" end="8363200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle291">但這是事實</p>
<p begin="8364000000t" end="8384400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle292">有很多小朋友不擅長運動</p>
<p begin="8385200000t" end="8401600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle293">還有一些連走路也不穩的嬰兒</p>
<p begin="8419200000t" end="8444400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle294">關於這個問題，我有個主意</p>
<p begin="8452400000t" end="8472800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle295">甚麼主意　　玩捉迷藏</p>
<p begin="8507200000t" end="8525200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle296">由諾曼負責捉人，大家逃走</p>
<p begin="8540800000t" end="8563200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle297">大家假裝在玩，其實是在訓練？</p>
<p begin="8570800000t" end="8588400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle298">這樣就不會被媽媽識破</p>
<p begin="8589200000t" end="8610000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle299">我會教他們運用身體的方法</p>
<p begin="8614400000t" end="8628000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle300">至於運用頭腦方面</p>
<p begin="8628800000t" end="8637200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle301">就交給我…</p>
<p begin="8705200000t" end="8715600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle302">不要焦急</p>
<p begin="8728800000t" end="8738000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle303">要思考一下</p>
<p begin="8738800000t" end="8755200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle304">怎樣做才可以逃脫</p>
<p begin="8762800000t" end="8780000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle305">諾曼是不會看漏這些腳印的</p>
<p begin="8870800000t" end="8880000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle306">感受風向</p>
<p begin="8887200000t" end="8902400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle307">哪個方向對逃走有利</p>
<p begin="8913600000t" end="8940800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle308">現在這邊是順風</p>
<p begin="9082000000t" end="9094400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle309">表現不錯</p>
<p begin="9095200000t" end="9120000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle310">現在他完全沒辦法可以捉到我</p>
<p begin="9120800000t" end="9139600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle311">照這樣下去我也可以成功…</p>
<p begin="9158800000t" end="9187600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle312">本來以為順利擺脫了他</p>
<p begin="9192800000t" end="9217600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle313">只是留下自己的痕跡是不足夠的</p>
<p begin="9218400000t" end="9237600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle314">還要留意對手的痕跡才行</p>
<p begin="9238400000t" end="9257600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle315">是這樣嗎　　對</p>
<p begin="9258400000t" end="9269600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle316">而且諾曼經常會留意到</p>
<p begin="9270400000t" end="9282800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle317">你們每一個人的習慣</p>
<p begin="9288400000t" end="9299200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle318">例如是托馬…</p>
<p begin="9420400000t" end="9448400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle319">捉迷藏好像很好玩</p>
<p begin="9449200000t" end="9476000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle320">我也想可以跟大家打成一片</p>
<p begin="9476800000t" end="9493600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle321">也讓我一起玩吧</p>
<p begin="9494400000t" end="9522800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle322">玩捉迷藏限時20分鐘定勝負</p>
<p begin="9523600000t" end="9542400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle323">我負責來捉你們</p>
<p begin="9543200000t" end="9568800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle324">大家要努力逃走</p>
<p begin="9585000000t" end="9634200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle325">7、8、9、10</p>
<p begin="9645800000t" end="9675800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle326">好，快些讓我見識一下</p>
<p begin="9676600000t" end="9706600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle327">見識那個女人特別的小朋友</p>
<p begin="9710200000t" end="9734200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle328">好，敵人會採取甚麼行動</p>
<p begin="9760200000t" end="9775400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle329">首先她會來找我們</p>
<p begin="9784200000t" end="9795800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle330">在找我們的途中</p>
<p begin="9796600000t" end="9813400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle331">將其他小朋友一網打盡</p>
<p begin="9814200000t" end="9825000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle332">應該就是這樣吧</p>
<p begin="9907000000t" end="9916200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle333">假鞋印？</p>
<p begin="9941400000t" end="9966200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle334">為甚麼會這麼安靜</p>
<p begin="9985400000t" end="10011400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle335">我要認真來捉你們</p>
<p begin="10117800000t" end="10131400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle336">完全沒有追上來</p>
<p begin="10132200000t" end="10143400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle337">她改變了策略？</p>
<p begin="10185400000t" end="10195800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle338">怎麼這樣　　就是了</p>
<p begin="10213800000t" end="10233800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle339">真可惜</p>
<p begin="10234600000t" end="10249000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle340">為甚麼他們會聚集</p>
<p begin="10260990000t" end="10280990000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle341">她用樹葉將小朋友引過去</p>
<p begin="10281800000t" end="10299000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle342">看來她並不是一個笨蛋</p>
<p begin="10404200000t" end="10429400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle343">不要</p>
<p begin="10499400000t" end="10528200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle344">大家聽我說，修女真的很厲害</p>
<p begin="10544600000t" end="10561800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle345">阿唐和吉爾妲也輸了</p>
<p begin="10567800000t" end="10580200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle346">真的很難應付</p>
<p begin="10581000000t" end="10601400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle347">無論去哪裡都被她追上</p>
<p begin="10602200000t" end="10616600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle348">而且還比諾曼</p>
<p begin="10617400000t" end="10636600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle349">負責捉人時的節奏快很多</p>
<p begin="10637400000t" end="10654200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle350">艾瑪</p>
<p begin="10665400000t" end="10677000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle351">掩著嘴巴</p>
<p begin="10788600000t" end="10816200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle352">我跳</p>
<p begin="10922600000t" end="10947800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle353">一直抱著他們不斷地跑</p>
<p begin="10948600000t" end="10970200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle354">你一定很累，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="10988200000t" end="11018600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle355">不休息一下就跑不動了吧</p>
<p begin="11019400000t" end="11028600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle356">我知道</p>
<p begin="11029400000t" end="11046600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle357">諾曼的弱點是他比較孱弱</p>
<p begin="11047400000t" end="11055800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle358">體力不足</p>
<p begin="11056600000t" end="11082200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle359">聽說他在很久之前，身體就很虛弱</p>
<p begin="11083000000t" end="11095000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle360">而阿雷的弱點</p>
<p begin="11095800000t" end="11116200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle361">就是他很快就會決定放棄</p>
<p begin="11121000000t" end="11134600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle362">判斷做得很快</p>
<p begin="11135400000t" end="11160600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle363">但同時亦很快捨棄事物</p>
<p begin="11161400000t" end="11183400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle364">接著到你了，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="11184200000t" end="11209800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle365">你的弱點就是太天真</p>
<p begin="11210600000t" end="11226600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle366">明明被人追著</p>
<p begin="11227400000t" end="11240200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle367">也要抱住其他小朋友</p>
<p begin="11241000000t" end="11260600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle368">一起逃走那麼天真</p>
<p begin="11267800000t" end="11295000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle369">你還是快些放棄，走出來</p>
<p begin="11295800000t" end="11315800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle370">我不會做令你難受的事</p>
<p begin="11326200000t" end="11339000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle371">對了，艾瑪</p>
<p begin="11339800000t" end="11356200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle372">如果你就是那天</p>
<p begin="11357000000t" end="11379000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle373">看到收穫的小朋友的話</p>
<p begin="11387000000t" end="11406600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle374">我是會站在你那邊</p>
<p begin="11437000000t" end="11458200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle375">終於找到你了</p>
<p begin="11477400000t" end="11487800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle376">還欠兩個人</p>
<p begin="11488600000t" end="11513400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle377">還有多少時間　　8分40秒</p>
<p begin="11676600000t" end="11709000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle378">這就是這裡的滿分小朋友</p>
<p begin="11768600000t" end="11777000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle379">時間到了</p>
<p begin="11849400000t" end="11887000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle380">諾曼、阿雷、艾瑪</p>
<p begin="11904200000t" end="11916600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle381">還有…</p>
<p begin="11961400000t" end="11972200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle382">自從那次之後</p>
<p begin="11973000000t" end="11993800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle383">修女就沒有對我們採取行動</p>
<p begin="12001800000t" end="12021800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle384">那麼這個一定是媽媽給她的指示</p>
<p begin="12027400000t" end="12052600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle385">媽媽最初也有試探我們</p>
<p begin="12053400000t" end="12068200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle386">但是現在就沒有這樣做</p>
<p begin="12069000000t" end="12081400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle387">為甚麼會這樣</p>
<p begin="12090600000t" end="12107800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle388">阿雷，你覺得怎樣</p>
<p begin="12108600000t" end="12127800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle389">你又有甚麼看法？諾曼</p>
<p begin="12136600000t" end="12163000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle390">我覺得媽媽為了不需要親自行動</p>
<p begin="12163800000t" end="12188600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle391">暗中早已做好安排　　即是怎樣</p>
<p begin="12195400000t" end="12209000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle392">你想想對媽媽來說</p>
<p begin="12209800000t" end="12225400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle393">最輕鬆的情況會是怎樣</p>
<p begin="12258600000t" end="12277800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle394">就是不用做任何事情</p>
<p begin="12278600000t" end="12295400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle395">也仍然可以知道我們的動向</p>
<p begin="12301800000t" end="12320200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle396">不過，這裡沒有監視攝影機</p>
<p begin="12321000000t" end="12333800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle397">也沒有竊聽器</p>
<p begin="12382600000t" end="12393400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle398">這即是說…</p>
<p begin="12401800000t" end="12417000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle399">沒錯，恐怕…</p>
<p begin="12417800000t" end="12438200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle400">恐怕已經有其他監視人員在這裡</p>
<p begin="12439000000t" end="12460200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle401">有可能就是在小朋友之中</p>
<p begin="12465800000t" end="12477400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle402">我們有內奸</p>
<p begin="12573000000t" end="12582600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle403">快走吧</p>
<p begin="12619000000t" end="12630200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle404">排隊</p>
<p begin="12910200000t" end="12934200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle405">(泛紅的天空)</p>
<p begin="12935000000t" end="12972200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle406">(如今看來如此恐怖)</p>
<p begin="12977400000t" end="12997000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle407">(若不知曉)</p>
<p begin="12997800000t" end="13032600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle408">(是否就能幸福度日)</p>
<p begin="13038600000t" end="13111400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle409">(又一盞溫暖的燈火悄悄熄滅)</p>
<p begin="13112200000t" end="13151400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle410">(不知不覺中失去了)</p>
<p begin="13152200000t" end="13211400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle411">(曾經誤信過　那溫柔的聲音)</p>
<p begin="13212200000t" end="13245800000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle412">(那曾是我的一切)</p>
<p begin="13246600000t" end="13312200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle413">(憑著揮灑的汗水與熾熱的心)</p>
<p begin="13313000000t" end="13380200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle414">(我們的確抱著意志生存)</p>
<p begin="13381000000t" end="13419000000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle415">(事到如今　還說甚麼想要你的愛)</p>
<p begin="13419800000t" end="13447400000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle416">(動起來　不聽使喚的雙腿)</p>
<p begin="13448200000t" end="13480600000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle417">(脫離這個牢籠)</p>
<p begin="13481400000t" end="13514200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle418">(抓緊明天的自由)</p>
<p begin="13515000000t" end="13546200000t" region="bottomCenter" style="s1" xml:id="subtitle419">(走出絕望的困境)</p>
</div>
